the big restaurant ( french : le grand restaurant ) , is a french comedy thriller film from 1966 , directed by jacques besnard , written by jean halain and louis de funès , starring louis de funès and bernard blier .   the film is known under the titles : " the big restaurant " ( international english title ) , " what ’s cooking in paris " ( usa ) , " el gran restaurante " ( spain ) , " das große restaurant " ( east germany ) , " oscar hat die hosen voll " ( west germany ) , " chi ha rubato il presidente ? "